gomodel:SYNGO_5341  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figuire 2: SIM super-resolution imaging of endogenous AnkG (ankyrin-G, gene ANK3) and Usp9X showed co-localization at/near dendritic spine heads. \"Most spines exhibited two or more ankyrin-G nanodomains surrounding Usp9X (Figure 2D).\". Experimental description: M&M: \"Dissociated cultures of primary cortical neurons were prepared from P0 C57BL/6J (The Jackson Laboratories) pups.\"\n\nantibody:\nMouse monoclonal anti-AnkG, NeuroMab Facility, Cat#75-146; RRID: AB_10673030\nGoat polyclonal anti-AnkG (P-20), Santa Cruz Biotechnology, Cat#sc-31778; RRID: AB_2289736\nRabbit polyclonal anti-Usp9X, Abcam, Cat#ab19879; RRID: AB_470300" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" ;
        dc:date           "2023-03-12" ;
